OL,6,F"Whilst overall demand is as our
OL,7,Fmodels have forecast, we have seen 70%
OL,8,Fof callers using 999 triaged as either
OL,9,Fa category 1 or category 2 emergency
OL,10,F(which is a higher proportion than
OL,11,Fexpected) meaning more patients
OL,12,Frequire an ambulance response and
OL,13,Ftransport to hospital."
OL,15,FThe service says the problem was made
OL,16,Fworse by delays in offloading patients.
