OL,6,FIt added: "This has happened at a time
OL,7,Fwhen we are experiencing challenges
OL,8,Fwith handover delays at acute
OL,9,Fhospitals across our region, which
OL,10,Fthen impacts our ability to respond
OL,11,Faccordingly.
OL,13,F"People calling 999 with lower acuity
OL,14,Fproblems (category 3 and 4 patients)
OL,15,Fare likely to be advised to seek
OL,16,Falternative care in order that we can
OL,17,Fincrease our ambulance availability
OL,18,Ffor patients with life-threatening
OL,19,Finjuries and illnesses."
